# Newsletter Includes — Single Line

The **INCLUDES** bar (icons + labels under pricing) must render as a **single horizontal line**. Items must not wrap onto a second row.

## Rules

- Keep includes compact: small type (~10px), small icons (~13px), tight horizontal padding
- Use `flex-wrap: nowrap` on `.nl-includes-items`
- Prefer shrinking size/padding over wrapping when more inclusions are added
- Do not enlarge includes type or icons without an explicit request
- Label (`INCLUDES:`) stays on the same bar; on narrow widths it may sit above the items row, but the items themselves stay one line

## Bad

```css
.nl-includes-items { flex-wrap: wrap; }
.nl-includes-item { font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 16px; }
```

## Good

```css
.nl-includes-items { flex-wrap: nowrap; }
.nl-includes-item { font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 10px; }
```
